<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Hartford Financial cut.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Hartford Financial cut.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Lehman Brothers said it downgraded Hartford Financial Services Group Inc to outperform from buy and removed the stock from the recommended list.</p>
<p>-- said still believes Hartford Financial shares are undervalued, but &quot;few strong catalysts remain that can drive rapid multiple expansion towards fair value.&quot;</p>
<p>-- set a one-year price target of $90 a share.</p>
<p>-- Hartford Financial lost 3/4 to 77-5/8.</p>
